-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                     MACCHIATO - Java Spam Library
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  
 Macchiato is an anti-spam library. It consists of text-retrieval, analysis
 tools and uses a naive bayesian machine-learning approach to improve automatic
 spam messages detection.

 For the latest information on new releases, website or ressource changes, 
 please visit http://columba.sourceforge.net


